    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that is usable and enjoyable as-is, but it clearly shows its age and is not a show car. The paint and body have visible blemishes, imperfections, and age-related wear, and the interior is presentable but worn in the ways you\u2019d expect from an older driver. It still has decent overall eye appeal from a distance, but up close you\u2019ll see the cosmetic shortcomings. A straightforward, honest example for someone who wants a usable car rather than a pristine one.",
