    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Project-grade example in poor overall condition and best suited for a buyer looking for a restoration candidate, parts car, or a vehicle to sort through over time. The exterior shows significant age and wear, with visible cosmetic flaws and a generally tired presentation. Expect the interior to need attention as well, with wear consistent with a heavily used and neglected vehicle. Mechanical needs should be assumed, and this is not something I would describe as a dependable driver without recommissioning and repairs. It may still have value for the right buyer, but please come expecting a rough car that will require work.",
