      "description": "Budget-priced vehicle in poor overall condition and best suited for someone looking for basic transportation with repairs in mind or a project car. It shows noticeable wear inside and out, including cosmetic blemishes, an aged interior, and signs of deferred maintenance. It runs and drives, but buyers should expect issues consistent with a worn, older vehicle and should plan on mechanical attention and cleanup. This is not a turnkey or especially clean example, but it could work for someone who wants an inexpensive vehicle and understands what a poor-condition car typically needs.",
